342
00:25:53,236 --> 00:25:55,319
[SPEAKER_03]: That is not a disincentive.

343
00:25:55,339 --> 00:25:57,963
[SPEAKER_03]: That is not a deterrent, and it's not working.

344
00:25:57,983 --> 00:26:01,869
