887
01:01:56,409 --> 01:01:58,432
[SPEAKER_10]: Julie's question is about mending the trading relationship with Europe.

888
01:01:58,452 --> 01:02:07,603
[SPEAKER_04]: And the second thing we'll do for you, for all those people like you who are self-employed and others in small businesses, I want to abolish your national insurance so that you have more financial security.

889
01:02:07,583 --> 01:02:11,191
[SPEAKER_04]: Now, I'm the person that has made sure that we have good relations with Europe.

890
01:02:11,231 --> 01:02:12,013
