891
01:02:12,254 --> 01:02:13,457
[SPEAKER_04]: And we will continue to do so.

892
01:02:13,697 --> 01:02:22,077
[SPEAKER_04]: But the best way I can help your small business and the hundreds of thousands of others like yours is to continue to cut your taxes, because that's how we'll give you financial security.

893
